<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-24-0205 </DOCNO><TEXT>A computer system for data acquisition and supervisory control of fermentationprocesses is based on low price standard PC hardware with add on boardsfor process interface. The system is suitable even for installation toexisting fermentation plants with analog instrumentation. Software isspecial tailored to fermentation processes, and the realized functionshave been taken over from an industrial proven system. Necessary flexibilityis achieved by extensive configuration procedures.</TEXT></DOC>